K mart Corp said its board approveda 17.6 pct increase in the quarterly dividend and declared athree-for-two stock split.    The company raised its dividend to 43.5 cts a presplitshare, up from the previous 37 cts a share. After the split,the new quarterly dividend rate is equivalent to 29 cts ashare. It is payable June Eight, record May 21.    It said the additional shares will be distributed JuneFive, record May 21. Reuter&#3;